                                                                                                                       7                                      DAY V HIGHLIGHTS
                      
	Indias score of 459 is the highest second innings total by a team who lost by an innings. Other teams to have been defeated by an innings after posting a high score are as follows:         
	South Africa: 434 vs Sri Lanka. Sri Lanka won by innings amp; 153 runs (2006 in Colombo)         
	Australia: 422 vs South Africa. South Africa won by an innings amp; 20 runs (2009 in Cape Town)         
	England: 417 vs South Africa. South Africa won by an innings amp; 92 runs (2003 in Lords)         
	South Africa: 390 vs England. England won by innings amp; 18 runs (1924 in Birmingham)         
	Mohandas Menon                                                                                                                     
